<text top="2006" left="1540" width="481" height="51" font="font8" id="p1_t112" reading_order_no="111" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">to  mass-produce  the  machine.</text>
<text top="2049" left="1590" width="620" height="51" font="font8" id="p1_t113" reading_order_no="112" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">A  life-saving  device  spawned  from</text>
